{"tid":1952351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"入酒吧無量體溫 14警涉違法","createTime":"2020-03-31T14:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T14:37:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4563fdb5f0fd566350f884f8067d67b8a4c7b319","tid":1952351,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200331/5ODKYYT2PYNC64GUFPJJEOOI7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200331%2F5ODKYYT2PYNC64GUFPJJEOOI7M%2F&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=2567becb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200331%2F5ODKYYT2PYNC64GUFPJJEOOI7M%2F&h=4c989318\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200331/5ODKYYT2PYNC64GUFPJJEOOI7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n入酒吧無量體溫 14警涉違法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200331/large/1585586819_2bfb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585586819_2bfb.gif&h=6ed46f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警員違規】新規例實施當晚，14名機動部隊成員無經酒吧職員（右）量度體溫便進入店內。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上周末生效的《預防及控制疾病（規定及指示）（業務及處所）規例》，要求餐飲處所為客人量體溫，但本報發現，負責執法的警務人員疑率先「違法」，未有量體溫就進入酒吧。餐飲業界表示不清楚警務人員是否需先量體溫，若對方拒絕，亦會無奈接受。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高拔陞：醫院爆煲 病人或回家隔離<br />\n<br />\n條例沒豁免<br />\n<br />\n為預防武漢肺炎在社區擴散，《規例》列明，在容許某人進入餐飲處所前，須先為該人量度體溫，條例沒有豁免。規例實施首日，本報記者到尖沙嘴諾士佛臺一帶酒吧街採訪，現場所見，酒吧職員主動為進入酒吧的七名食環署職員量度體溫，但隨後有警務人員入內時，職員主動放下電子體溫計，並揚手指示14名警務人員入場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200331/large/1585586819_efd9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585586819_efd9.gif&h=1000c0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【食環守法】食環署職員入內前接受店員量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n執法人員是否受條例規管？本報向訂立規例的食衞局查詢，截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日，已先後有三名警員確診武漢肺炎。香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華說，不知道警務人員可否豁免量體溫，「咁佢唔俾我量，我又可以點呢？無奈接受！」<br />\n<br />\n酒吧業協會副主席錢雋永同樣不清楚是否有豁免，他呼籲業界為所有進入酒吧的人士量體溫，至於若遇上有執法人員拒絕配合，要與業界商討如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張雅婷"},{"pid":"744d0d33fe4a845dd4dbe2477458969de98a3e3a","tid":1952351,"uid":105340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"唔會違法 仲要3萬個THX"},{"pid":"393a3fcca422484ea8179350c26e4aea23849ebf","tid":1952351,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"進入酒吧的<span style=\"color: red;\">人士</span>"},{"pid":"8982db2b6c2bd471067272c9e77ca85c0f63e1e1","tid":1952351,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f33294ba53555b48ab2f488d7439d8067efe9e28","tid":1952351,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"做到最後最多咪<br />\n又係訓斥就算"},{"pid":"127b50131e80171da23cba7597fbbf05ae12824b","tid":1952351,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"393a3fcca422484ea8179350c26e4aea23849ebf","tid":1952351,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"進入酒吧的<span style=\"color: red;\">人士</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"唔識點幫畜生量體溫，咪放佢入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2729901e33173ff6b9e65cbe56670a967dc72f","tid":1952351,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"伙計做野太投入忘記左量體溫"},{"pid":"84099f17a61f15eebea168958abf56a39e2da81d","tid":1952351,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b70abb08097d9460b1027b5f0ae5c053009f42ed","tid":1952351,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"狗唔計"},{"pid":"058c307a03dedb61849ceb580cea8132fbbf8ad5","tid":